with little effort, and i's even semi-interactive (hover your pointer over the legend!):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code rest"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;..&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;chart&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; StackedLine
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:title:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;'Browser usage evolution (in %)'&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:fill:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:x_labels:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;['2002','2003','2004','2005','2006','2007','2008','2009','2010','2011','2012']&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:width:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;600&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:height:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;400&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-7"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:explicit_size:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;True&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-8"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class="nc"&gt;:style:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nf"&gt;DefaultStyle&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-9"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-10"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   ('Others',  [14.2, 15.4, 15.3,  8.9,    9, 10.4,  8.9,  5.8,  6.7,  6.8,  7.5])
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-11"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   ('IE',      [85.8, 84.6, 84.7, 74.5,   66, 58.6, 54.7, 44.8, 36.2, 26.6, 20.1])
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-12"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   ('Firefox', [None, None, None, 16.6,   25,   31, 36.4, 45.5, 46.3, 42.8, 37.1])
&lt;a name="rest_code_307bb68a4d2b4746b2cececb48a7a40c-13"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   ('Chrome',  [None, None, None, None, None, None,    0,  3.9, 10.8, 23.8, 35.3])
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macplay.github.io/posts/pygal-charts-get-started/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (3 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>charts</category><category>pygal</category><category>python</category><category>reST</category><guid>https://macplay.github.io/posts/pygal-charts-get-started/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 18 Sep 2017 03:09:34 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>